    "en": {
      "title": "A young man who stole goods from Ranil's house is remanded till 10",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage ordered today (2) to remand a 22-year-old youth who was arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department for breaking into President Ranil Wickramasinghe's residence and stealing goods until the 10th for an identification parade.",
        "The court also ordered the release of the two minors who were arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department in connection with this incident on two surety bonds of five lakh rupees each.",
        "The court also canceled the identification parade of these two minor children."
      ],
